title: The moment the Senate rebukes Elizabeth Warren
text: The moment the Senate rebukes Elizabeth Warren The Senate rebuked Sen. Elizabeth Warren for quoting Coretta Scott King. Warren read King's words criticizing Senator Jeff Sessions when he was considered for a federal judgeship in 1984. Sessions is now being considered for Attorney General.
